<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
 <head>
   <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
 </head>
 <body>
 <center><h4>Leave request pending for approval </h4></center>

 <p>There is a leave request pending for your approval in People First HRMS.</p>

<p><h4> Details of the Leave:- </h4></p>

 <p>Employee ID :- <%= @leave_request.employee.manual_employee_code %></p>
 <p>Employee Name :- <%= @leave_request.employee.try(:prefix) %> <%= @leave_request.employee.first_name %> <%= @leave_request.employee.try(:middle_name) %> <%= @leave_request.employee.try(:last_name) %></p>
 <p>Leave Category :- <%= @leave_request.leav_category.name %></p>
 <p>From Date :- <%= @leave_request.start_date.to_date %>
 To Date :- <%= @leave_request.end_date.to_date%></p>
 <p>Total Number of days :- <%= @leave_request.leave_count %></p>
<p> Leave Reason :- <%= @leave_request.reason %></p>

 </body>
</html>